### Obtener artistas

GET http://localhost:8000/artistas HTTP/1.1

### Obtener un artista por id

GET http://localhost:8000/artistas/2 HTTP/1.1

### Crear un artista

POST http://localhost:8000/artistas HTTP/1.1
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "nombre": "Bege"
}

### Actualizar un artista

PUT http://localhost:8000/artistas/3 HTTP/1.1
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "nombre": "Aiekas"
}

### Eliminar un artista

DELETE http://localhost:8000/artistas/3 HTTP/1.1

### Obtener albumes

GET http://localhost:8000/albumes HTTP/1.1

### Obtener un album por id

GET http://localhost:8000/albumes/1 HTTP/1.1

### Crear un album

POST http://localhost:8000/albumes HTTP/1.1
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "nombre": "Beges",
  "artista": 2
}

### Actualizar un album

PUT http://localhost:8000/albumes/1 HTTP/1.1
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "nombre": "Megma",
  "artista": 2
}

### Eliminar un album

DELETE http://localhost:8000/albumes/3 HTTP/1.1

### Obtener canciones

GET http://localhost:8000/canciones HTTP/1.1

### Obtener una cancion por id

GET http://localhost:8000/canciones/1 HTTP/1.1

### Crear una cancion

POST http://localhost:8000/canciones HTTP/1.1
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "nombre": "Megma",
  "album": 1,
  "duracion": 300
}

### Actualizar una cancion

PUT http://localhost:8000/canciones/3 HTTP/1.1
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "nombre": "Cancion 2",
  "album": 1,
  "duracion": 260
}

### Eliminar una cancion

DELETE http://localhost:8000/canciones/1 HTTP/1.1

